# DO NOT gitignore .brain/ — codebrain commits the brain by default (PRD Design Decision #3).
# The wiki's compounding-artifact property requires version history + team sharing.
# If a contributor wants the brain gitignored, that's a deliberate `codebrain init --private`
# decision, not a default.
